alfonsino
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:Bright red and silver midwater marine fishes, fam. Berycidae, widely distributed in the world's oceans, in NZ esp. the slender beryx <i>Beryx splendens</i>, and the longfinned beryx <i>B. decadactylus. </i>
